<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ظ أر:</span> <span class="c2">(الظِّئْرُ)</span> مَكْسُورٌ مَهْمُوزٌ وَجَمْعُهُ <span class="c2">(ظُؤَارٌ)</span> بِالضَّمِّ كَفُعَالٍ وَ <span class="c2">(ظُئُورٌ)</span> كَفُلُوسٍ وَأَظْآرٌ كَأَحْمَالٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>